<CATEGORY> entertainment </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Garofalo on 'Mad About You' Finale </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Cross Helen Hunt with Paul Reiser and you get --  
Janeane Garofalo? 
</P>
<P>
	The comedian will appear as a grown-up version of Jamie and Paul  
Buchman's daughter, Mabel, on the final episode of ``Mad About 
You.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Hunt, who plays Jamie, will direct the one-hour May 24 finale.  
After seven seasons on the show, Hunt tells the April 24 edition of 
TV Guide, ``I wanted to be actively involved in the end rather that 
let it happen to me.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Hunt also wrote the story with Reiser, her co-star and  
co-executive producer, and with executive producer Victor Levin. 
</P>
</TEXT>
