<HEADLINE> Shut Out Time Wins at Aqueduct </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Shut Out Time and Winloc's Glorious each won  
divisions of the sixth running of the $100,000 New York Stallion 
Stakes for 3-year-olds at Aqueduct today. 
</P>
<P>
