<TEXT>
<P>
	HONG KONG (AP) -- French entry Jim and Tonic set a record in  
winning the $679,489 Audemars Piguet Queen Elizabeth II Cup on 
Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
	Jim and Tonic, ridden by Herald Mosse, finished the 2,000-meter  
