said. ``But I think it's better for the women to run on their 
own.'' 
</P>
<P>
	Manuela Machado, a Portuguese world champion marathon runner who  
placed third behind Chepchumba and Adriana Fernandez of Mexico, 
agreed the Loroupe's performance in Rotterdam last year was not as 
good. 
